sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ<br/>(queue: balance.transaction-registered)
    participant Cons as TransactionConsumer
    participant Polly as Polly ResiliencePipeline<br/>("consumer-pipeline")
    participant Svc as ConsolidationService
    participant UoW as IUnitOfWork
    participant Events as IProcessedEventsRepository
    participant BalanceRepo as IBalanceRepository
    participant Dom as DailyBalance<br/>(Rich Domain)

    MQ->>Cons: TransactionRegistered<br/>(at-least-once delivery)
    Cons->>Polly: ExecuteAsync(handler)
    Note over Polly: Retry 3x exp backoff + jitter

    Polly->>Svc: ApplyAsync(evt, consumerName)
    Svc->>UoW: BeginAsync()

    Svc->>Events: ExistsAsync(EventId, consumerName)
    alt Já processado (idempotência)
        Events-->>Svc: true
        Svc->>UoW: CommitAsync()
        Note over Svc: return — não reaplica
    else Novo evento
        Events-->>Svc: false
        Svc->>BalanceRepo: GetByDateAsync(evt.MovementDate)
        BalanceRepo-->>Svc: DailyBalance ou null
        Svc->>Dom: ApplyCredit/ApplyDebit(evt.Amount)
        Svc->>BalanceRepo: UpsertAsync(balance)
        Svc->>Events: RegisterAsync(EventId, consumerName)
        Svc->>UoW: CommitAsync()
        Note over UoW: Atomic — saldo + marcador<br/>na mesma transação
    end

    Polly-->>Cons: OK
    Cons->>MQ: Ack
    Note over MQ: mensagem removida da fila
